  "2026-06-03T15:02:21.424Z",claude-code-agent,"COMPLETION RECORD (kept open intentionally): all scoped work delivered & closed — pm-k8ik (remove-type), pm-e77a (add-status/remove-status), pm-f4r1 (per-type workflows), pm-jpwo (config create_default_type), pm-mt7k + pm-vhd9 (satisfied stories). Full coverage gate green (2195 tests, 100%), static gate green, smoke-tested end-to-end. Left in 'open' status (not closed) so this coordination Plan stays OUT of the closed-items CHANGELOG (pm-changelog buckets only closed items; a Plan is an organizational container, not a shippable change). Tracked under epic pm-8jdc."
  "2026-06-03T15:06:53.892Z",claude-code-agent,"PR opened: https://github.com/unbraind/pm-cli/pull/106 (branch schema-customization-completion-20260603, commit 3f7f9867). Triggered @codex / @gemini-code-assist / CodeRabbit review. Awaiting CI + 20-min AI bot review window."
  "2026-06-03T22:39:45.967Z",claude-code-agent,"Review round 1 addressed (commit a9b38d74): fixed status add-status data-loss (roles/aliases preserved unless explicitly set), per-type-workflow explicit-empty deny-all (the file-load normalizer was stripping it), non-finite --order rejection (CLI+MCP), clearable governance-create-default-type, gated orphan-removal warnings, settings-reuse perf, defensive guards. Skipped 4 with reasons (auto-gen CHANGELOG bucket, dead-code spread guard, correct docs link, too-invasive contract narrowing). Full coverage gate 2203 tests/100%, static green. Re-triggered @codex/@gemini-code-assist/CodeRabbit; awaiting round-2."
  "2026-06-04T00:03:33.897Z",claude-code-agent,"MERGED: PR #106 merged to main 2026-06-03 (merge commit 5c055d69). All 6 schema-epic items closed (pm-k8ik/e77a/f4r1/jpwo + stories pm-mt7k/vhd9). Converged after 6 AI-review rounds: Codex clean x3 (rounds 4-6), Gemini 'no review comments' (round 6), CodeRabbit clean; all CI green; coverage 100%. 8 real review findings fixed (2 data-loss bugs, deny-all semantics, lifecycle-token shadowing, add-status TOCTOU, built-in-id override, malformed-workflow drop, post-update-type, NaN/fractional order, config clear, perf, defensive guards). 1 pre-existing cross-cutting bug deferred + tracked as pm-haak. Telemetry stack healthy/real-time (16.1k events/24h); Sentry has no new issues from this PR. Daily auto-release will cut the next version from the non-empty CHANGELOG [Unreleased]."
  "2026-06-06T20:08:08.275Z",codex-zw0n,"Reconciliation note during pm-zw0n cycle: pm-z5nb remains intentionally open as a coordination container (already merged work evidence in history/comments) and should stay open unless maintainers want this plan-type tracker item closed; no outstanding schema-customization implementation debt discovered in this cycle."
